    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dings, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still firm and free of any creases, and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by authorized technicians. For a collector or a discerning driver, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in perfect, original condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
