    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard. It features a refined interior paired with a robust powertrain, offering a balanced synthesis of luxury and dependable performance. This selection represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a high-caliber vehicle with a documented history of care. Experience the perfect intersection of prestige and value.",
