    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in great, reliable shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways, it runs like a dream and is ready to go whenever you are! I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014I think you'll really like what you see.",
