    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power through a functional M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a visceral induction note. A true driver\u2019s specimen that balances raw performance with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
